node.text: Thank you to @ardenfilmco for capturing such a special day in our lives 💕 We’re so incredibly happy we went with them to film our big day! There were so many small, special moments throughout the day that we both had forgotten about and @ardenfilmco was able to capture them for us. And of course, happy Valentine’s Day to my hubby @cmdorsch on our first Valentine’s Day as a married couple! I love you so much!!! node.text: Well, we officially have a six month old on our hands! 😱 My how the time flies. It feels like just yesterday we were on our way home from the hospital, and I couldn’t stop staring at our teeny tiny newborn. Kennedy, you are truly the light of our lives! You are a such a happy baby, but VERY inquisitive, and we are all in trouble when you decide to start crawling! You love tummy time, being read to (although you always want to eat the books), jumping in your jolly jumper, and being on-the-go. You still dislike naps, but love your nighttime sleep. Mommy and Daddy and your whole family love you beyond measure. ❤️ http://liketk.it/3jWBZ #LTKunder50 #LTKsalealert #LTKbaby #sixmonthsold #highlandsnc #mountaintrip
